creator: Parsable Inc
descriptionHtml:
Parsable empowers your team to get the job done right, every time by providing the tools needed to digitize, execute, measure, and transform work.

This connected-work approach is how companies mobilize their teams, flawlessly execute work, see what’s trending in real time, and learn and grow on the go, which boosts productivity, quality and safety.

Features:
* Easy-to-Build Templates - Transform your checklists, forms, and SOPs in minutes using no-code drag-and-drop components.
* Team Management - Build your team and assign custom roles to make sure the right information is available to the right team members.
* Work Execution - Transition seamlessly from your mobile device to your browser without skipping a beat. Team members can even share mobile devices to collaborate offline.
* Instant Video Calling - Share your surroundings (or your screen) with remote experts or teammates to get real-time guidance whenever needed.
* Integrate - Connect to existing systems and data sources to integrate and exchange data with enterprise applications that are part of your ecosystem.
* Analytics & Data Exports - Connect our data pipeline to your existing BI solution, or use the Parsable analytics capabilities that come out of the box.
* Reports & Audits - Generate a report or perform an audit whenever needed.
* Security & Privacy - Rest assured that your data is yours, and it will always be that way.

Use Cases

As a flexible, Mobile Collaboration & Workflow Platform, you are only limited by your imagination.

Field Operations, Process Efficiency, Process Transparency
* Manage Changeover
* Value-Added Process Transparency & Reporting
* Inspect Rented/Leased Equipment
* Journey Management
* Job Safety Analysis (JSA)

Quality, Safety, Training
* Product Inspections
* Remote Inspection
* Receiving Inspection
* Issue Management
* Lock Out / Tag Out
* Precision Work Execution
* Mobile OJT Training
* Competency Assessment

Managerial and General
* 3rd Party Inspection
* General Maintenance
* Preventative Maintenance
* Complex Assembly/Disassembly
* Continuous Improvement Management
* Best Practice Propagation

Parsable empowers your team to get the job done right, every time by providing the tools needed to digitize, execute, measure, and transform work.

This connected-work approach is how companies mobilize their teams, flawlessly execute work, see what’s trending in real time, and learn and grow on the go, which boosts productivity, quality and safety.

Features:
* Easy-to-Build Templates - Transform your checklists, forms, and SOPs in minutes using no-code drag-and-drop components.
* Team Management - Build your team and assign custom roles to make sure the right information is available to the right team members.
* Work Execution - Transition seamlessly from your mobile device to your browser without skipping a beat. Team members can even share mobile devices to collaborate offline.
* Integrate - Connect to existing systems and data sources to integrate and exchange data with enterprise applications that are part of your ecosystem.
* Analytics & Data Exports - Connect our data pipeline to your existing BI solution, or use the Parsable analytics capabilities that come out of the box.
* Reports & Audits - Generate a report or perform an audit whenever needed.
* Security & Privacy - Rest assured that your data is yours, and it will always be that way.

Use Cases

As a flexible, Mobile Collaboration & Workflow Platform, you are only limited by your imagination.

Field Operations, Process Efficiency, Process Transparency
* Manage Changeover
